## Component Roles & Interactions

### 1. Document Upload & Parsing Flow
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Router as routers.project_routes
    participant DocSvc as DocumentService
    participant ParserFactory as DocumentParserFactory
    participant StratFactory as DocumentProcessorFactory
    participant Storage as StorageService

    Client->>Router: POST /projects/{id}/documents
    Router->>DocSvc: upload_document(project_id, filename, contents, category)
    DocSvc->>StratFactory: get_strategy(filename, category)
    StratFactory-->>DocSvc: PdfProcessingStrategy
    DocSvc->>Storage: prepare_document_paths(project_id, filename, ext, category)
    Storage-->>DocSvc: (doc_id, file_path, spec_path)
    DocSvc->>Storage: save_pdf(file_path, contents)
    DocSvc->>ParserFactory: create()
    ParserFactory-->>DocSvc: PyMuPDFParser
    DocSvc->>Storage: register_document(...)
    Note over DocSvc, Storage: Document status set to "uploaded"
    DocSvc-->>Client: Upload Status Response
```

### 2. Analysis & Extraction Flow
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Router as routers.project_routes
    participant DocSvc as DocumentService
    participant Extractor as EquipmentExtractor
    participant LLM as LLM Factory & Strategy
    participant Storage as StorageService

    Client->>Router: POST /projects/{id}/documents/{doc_id}/analyze
    Router->>DocSvc: analyze_document(project_id, document_id)
    DocSvc->>Storage: get_document(project_id, document_id)
    DocSvc->>Extractor: extract(pdf_text, section_csvs)
    Extractor->>LLM: get_model(temperature=0, json=True)
    LLM-->>Extractor: ChatGroq (or Gemini, Ollama)
    Extractor->>LLM: invoke(prompt)
    LLM-->>Extractor: Extracted Spec JSON
    Extractor-->>DocSvc: EquipmentSpec Pydantic Object
    DocSvc->>Storage: save_spec_json(json_path, spec)
    DocSvc->>Storage: complete_extraction(project_id, doc_id, spec)
    Note over DocSvc, Storage: Document status set to "completed"
    DocSvc-->>Client: Extraction Result Spec
```

### 3. MES Tag Mapping Flow
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant AutoMapSvc as AutoMapService
    participant RerankSvc as RerankService
    participant LLM as BaseChatModel
    participant VectorStore as VectorStoreManager
    participant Storage as StorageService

    Client->>AutoMapSvc: run(project_id, family, template)
    AutoMapSvc->>Storage: Load EquipmentSpec & Template JSON
    AutoMapSvc->>VectorStore: Embed Tag Descriptions & Cosine Similarity
    VectorStore-->>AutoMapSvc: Top K Candidate Mappings
    Note over AutoMapSvc: Filter candidates by hard compatibility rules
    alt Cosine Score is high and gap is large
        Note over AutoMapSvc: Auto-accept suggestion (Method: vector)
    else Cosine Score is ambiguous (middle band)
        AutoMapSvc->>RerankSvc: rerank(tag, candidates)
        RerankSvc->>LLM: invoke(rerank_prompt)
        LLM-->>RerankSvc: Best matching candidate & confidence
        RerankSvc-->>AutoMapSvc: RerankResult
    end
    AutoMapSvc->>Storage: save_automap_result(...)
    AutoMapSvc-->>Client: AutoMapResponse
```
